<h1>How To Order</h1>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<h2>Direct call orders</h2>
<p>Call us (+302467024004) and you will receive the goods</p>
<ul>
<li>cash on delivery (valued only for Greece)</li>
<li>or with payment in advance in our bank accounts in ALPHA BANK, EUROBANK, CITIBANK</li>
<li>for special orders 20% prepayment is required in our bank accounts and the other 80% can be paid cash on delivery or deposit in a bank</li>
</ul>
<h2>Purchase</h2>
<p>When placing an order, the agreement of purchase is reached when your payment has been transferred.</p>
<h3>Card payment</h3>
<p>Furhome.gr handles secure phone call payments in collaboration with EUROBANK.</p>
<p>Card payment is a safe method of payment for you as a customer.</p>
<h3>Advance payment</h3>
<p>If you don't like to use a credit card you may transfer the money direct to our bank account.</p>
<p>In that case we will sent you a pro-forma invoice with all details.</p>
<p>You have to pay the complete amount in 5 days or you order will be discarded. Always state your order number when paying. We will send the products as soon as your payment is received.</p>
<h2>Prices</h2>
<p>All prices, include VAT<br /> 19% VAT is applied on sales in all EU countries.<br /> For non EU countries please contact our offices.</p>
<h2>Shipping</h2>
<p><strong>Greece</strong>: No shipping cost if your order value is more than 300.00 €, VAT included.<br /> If your order value is less than 300.00 € delivery cost is 12.00 €</p>
<p><strong>European Community</strong>:</p>
<p><strong>Rest of world</strong>: For the rest of the world please contact our offices.</p>
<h3>Delivery-time</h3>
<p>Normal delivery-time is 1-5 working-days within the EU and 2-10 working-days to other parts of the world.</p>
<h2>Warranty</h2>
<p>You have warranty on all products bought from us. The warranty is applicable for 1 year from the date you receive your products.</p>
<p>If the customer refers to the warranty and it is judged that the damage depends on bad handling by the customer the customer will pay the costs of any reparation. Our expert staff will in the first place determine the cause of the damage. The customer pays all shipping costs in case of warranty reparations.</p>
<h3>10 days purchase on approval / Satisfied customer warranty</h3>
<p>As a Fur Home shopper you have 10 days purchase on approval. You may return any of the products you bought from us within 10 days and get your money back. The products have to be in unaltered condition and should not have been used. You have to package them the same way as it was when you received them. Read more on return below. The customer pays for the shipping costs in both directions. 10 days purchase on approval only applies to shipments within the EU. The 10 days purchase on approval does not apply to companies.</p>
<h3>The right to exchange goods if you are not satisfied</h3>
<p>You have the right to change the products you bought if you are not satisfied with your purchase. Please contact our customer service department and they will help you with your change. The products have to be in the same condition as when you bought it and they should have not been used. The customer is responsible for both costs of shipping; that is onward and return shipping. The right to exchange goods if not satisfied applies only to deliveries made within the EU.</p>
<h2>Return</h2>
<p>When sending back a product you first have to contact Fur Home to get a return dispatch note. It is your responsibility that the product arrives in an undamaged condition. Make sure that the carpet is well packed. The return is not completed until we have received and examined the returned goods. When a return is completed the same card you used for the purchase will be credited.</p>
<p>If we receive products without the proper return dispatch note the goods will be sent back at the customer's expense.</p>
<h3>Error on delivery</h3>
<p>If something is wrong with your delivery, or if you receive the wrong product, a damaged product or the wrong number of products, please contact customer service immediately. The error has to be reported no later than two days after the goods have been received, reports received later will not be taken into consideration.</p>
<h3>Transportation damages</h3>
<p>Visible damage to the goods shall be reported directly to the courier when receiving the package. Hidden damages from transportation have to be reported to the courier company as soon as they are discovered.</p>
</div>
</div>

